                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18131027-107-off642 t18131027-107-crimeloc645"></join>. On the 20th of October, this man came in; he had a quantity of leather shewn; he pointed for it; I had suspicion of him. About nine o'clock he came again; I came down stairs, and watched him; he secreted these five pieces of leather under his coat. They are my property.</p>
